summary: Tommaso is an enthusiastic software developer; he discovered programming at a young age using an old Amstrad CPC464, since then he never stopped learning and creating new programs. While studying at high school he started focusing on web development; he started his own software company right after his studies when he was 19. Before founding Stream he worked together with Thierry at Fashiolista as Lead Engineer for a few years, where he co-authored the open source Stream-Framework library and others related to Python, Django and Apache Cassandra.
